Package com.enjin.sdk.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionEventListener
    Listener for receiving notifications about the connection state of the event service.
    EventMatcher
    Matches events.
    NotificationListener
    Notification event listener.
    NotificationsService
    Notification service interface for subscribing to and registering for events from the Enjin Cloud.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NotificationListenerRegistration
    Registration wrapper for a NotificationListener that extracts any metadata from the notification listener that may be used in event handling.
    NotificationListenerRegistration.RegistrationListenerConfiguration<T extends NotificationListenerRegistration.RegistrationListenerConfiguration<T>>
    A registration configuration for listeners.
    PusherEventListener
    Event listener class for subscribed pusher events.
    PusherNotificationService
    Implementation class of NotificationsService utilizing Pusher channel events.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    EventFilter
    Indicates the events to be filtered by the type.
